article.headline: Thomas scores 31 as Norfolk State beats Illinois State 64-58
article.description: — Jamarii Thomas' 31 points led Norfolk State over Illinois State 64-58 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Thomas scores 31 as Norfolk State beats Illinois State 64-58
article.story: NORMAL, Ill. -- — Jamarii Thomas' 31 points led Norfolk State over Illinois State 64-58 on Saturday night. Thomas added six rebounds and three steals for the Spartans (7-3). Allen Betrand was 4-of-10 shooting (2 for 4 from 3-point range) to add 12 points. Johnny Kinziger led the way for the Redbirds (6-4) with 13 points. Myles Foster added 11 points, 10 rebounds and two steals for Illinois State. In addition, Darius Burford had 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
